docs.lead_paragraph: The American aid worker who spent five years in prison in Cuba said he had no trouble bringing sophisticated communications gear into the country and made little attempt to disguise his work to set up Internet connections.

docs.lead_paragraph: When it comes to food, the simple rules are still the best.

headline.main: Could Your Healthy Diet Make Me Fat?
headline.print_headline: Could Your Healthy Diet Make Me Fat?

docs.abstract: Op-Ed article by David S Ludwig highlights study published by Weizmann Institute of Science that suggests personalized nutrition could supplant and be more effective than conventional diet regimens; discusses his own research into issue of obesity and diet, and suggests personalized nutrition should build upon, rather than completely substitute, national dietary guidelines.
docs.snippet: When it comes to food, the simple rules are still the best.

docs.lead_paragraph: Stephen Cheuk runs S10 Training, a downtown Manhattan gym with a stylish male clientele.

headline.main: A New York Trainer to Men About Town
headline.print_headline: The Trainer to Men of Style

docs.abstract: Stephen Cheuk, personal trainer to stylish men, has become known for his holistic approach to working out in order to both build more efficient body and look better; Cheuk is founder of S10 Training in Lower Manhattan.
